title: Louisiana couple arrested after deserting daughter, 5 | Daily Mail Online
text: Couple who gave their daughter, five, to a stranger on Valentineâ€™s Day and then VANISHED are arrested Shane White, 37, and Lacey Allen, 32, from Baton Rouge, allegedly left their daughter with a stranger Officers visited the motel where the couple were living and found it was 'filthy' Their other daughter, two, was found in a vehicle piled with used diapers The couple were arrested and charged with child desertion and two counts of cruelty to juveniles Published: 12:06 GMT, 17 February 2017 | Updated: 15:31 GMT, 17 February 2017 79 shares
